---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Website Beveiliging — LaventeCare"
  description="Veilige websites zijn onze standaard. Ontdek hoe wij uw data beschermen met input validatie, versleutelde opslag en continue monitoring."
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-24">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-20 text-center md:text-left">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start space-x-3 mb-6">
        <div class="h-px bg-active w-12"></div>
        <span class="text-active font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm font-display"
          >Beveiliging</span
        >
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white mb-8 font-display tracking-tight">
        Hoe wij uw website beveiligen
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/70 font-ui leading-relaxed">
        In een wereld vol cyberdreigingen is "goed genoeg" niet meer voldoende. Wij hanteren de
        hoogste standaarden voor uw data-integriteit en veiligheid, gebaseerd op onze 5
        beveiligingsprincipes.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- The 5 Laws -->
    <div class="mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-12 text-center md:text-left font-display">
        De 5 Beveiligingsprincipes
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Law 1 -->
        <div
          class="clinical-glass p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-active/50 transition-colors group fade-in-up"
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-active/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-active" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display">1. Alle invoer is verdacht</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4 font-ui">
            Wij vertrouwen niets. Elke input, elke parameter en elke header wordt beschouwd als
            vijandig totdat het tegendeel is bewezen via strikte validatie.
          </p>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/40 font-mono bg-black/20 p-2 rounded">
            Strikte invoervalidatie
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Law 2 -->
        <div
          class="clinical-glass p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-active/50 transition-colors group fade-in-up"
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-active/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-active" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display">2. Geen informatie lekken</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4 font-ui">
            Wij lekken nooit interne informatie. Foutmeldingen zijn generiek voor de buitenwereld,
            maar kristalhelder in onze beveiligde audit logs.
          </p>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/40 font-mono bg-black/20 p-2 rounded">
            Veilige foutafhandeling
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Law 3 -->
        <div
          class="clinical-glass p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-active/50 transition-colors group fade-in-up"
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-active/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-active" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4m0 5c0 2.21-3.582 4-8 4s-8-1.79-8-4"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display">3. Database als kluis</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4 font-ui">
            SQL Injection is wiskundig onmogelijk gemaakt. Uw data is geïsoleerd op query-niveau,
            alsof elke klant zijn eigen kluis heeft.
          </p>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/40 font-mono bg-black/20 p-2 rounded">
            Veilige queries & data-isolatie
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Law 4 -->
        <div
          class="clinical-glass p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-active/50 transition-colors group fade-in-up"
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-active/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-active" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display">
            4. Bescherming tegen conflicten
          </h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4 font-ui">
            In een snelle omgeving telt elke milliseconde. Wij beschermen de staat van uw applicatie
            rigoureus tegen conflicten, zelfs onder zware belasting.
          </p>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/40 font-mono bg-black/20 p-2 rounded">
            Stateless afhandeling & vergrendeling
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Law 5 -->
        <div
          class="clinical-glass p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-active/50 transition-colors group fade-in-up"
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-active/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-active" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M20 7l-8-4-8 4m16 0l-8 4m8-4v10l-8 4m0-10L4 7m8 4v10M4 7v10l8 4"></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display">
            5. Minimale afhankelijkheden
          </h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4 font-ui">
            Wij bouwen op bewezen technologie, niet op de "flavor of the month". Minimale
            afhankelijkheden betekenen maximale stabiliteit en veiligheid.
          </p>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/40 font-mono bg-black/20 p-2 rounded">
            Bewezen technologie eerst
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Database Fortress & Compliance Detail -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto items-start">
      <div class="md:col-span-7 clinical-glass p-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/10">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center font-display">
          <svg
            class="w-8 h-8 text-active mr-4"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4m0 5c0 2.21-3.582 4-8 4s-8-1.79-8-4"
            ></path></svg
          >
          Technische Verdieping: <span class="text-active">Data-isolatie</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/70 mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed font-ui">
          Onze <strong>PostgreSQL</strong> database gebruikt <span class="text-white font-bold"
            >Row Level Security (RLS)</span
          >. Dit betekent dat de database <span class="text-active italic">*zelf*</span> handhaaft wie
          welke data mag zien. Zelfs als de applicatielogic zou falen (wat we voorkomen via Wet #1), weigert
          de database simpelweg data te tonen aan de verkeerde gebruiker.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start text-white/80 font-ui">
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
            >
            <span>Diepe verdedigingslinie (meerdere beveiligingslagen)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start text-white/80 font-ui">
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
            >
            <span
              >Automatische <span class="text-white font-medium">encryptie</span> van gevoelige velden</span
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-5 clinical-glass p-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center font-display">
          <svg
            class="w-8 h-8 text-active mr-4"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"
            ></path></svg
          >
          Logboek & Naleving
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/70 mb-6">
          Compliance is geen vinkje, het is een mindset. Elke kritieke actie in het systeem laat een
          onuitwisbaar spoor achter.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div
            class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 rounded bg-white/5 border border-white/10"
          >
            <span class="text-white/60 text-sm">Inlogpoging</span>
            <span class="text-active text-xs font-mono">2026-01-29 19:42:01 UTC</span>
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 rounded bg-white/5 border border-white/10"
          >
            <span class="text-white/60 text-sm">Beleidswijziging</span>
            <span class="text-active text-xs font-mono">2026-01-29 19:45:12 UTC</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
